de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization

Class BaseStation

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization.BaseStation

  • class BaseStation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to store the data received/pulled from main server. Contents are updated based on the corresponding mmsi's if already present in internal db else a new entry is added with all the values.
